&lt;h1&gt;MJF Hop Blend&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;2025 Michael James Jackson Foundation Hop Blend Profile&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This exclusive blend was created by the MJF board members at an event hosted by &lt;a title=&quot;Brooklyn Brewery&quot; href=&quot;https://brooklynbrewery.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Brooklyn Brewery&lt;/a&gt;. 16 different varieties were evaluated, blended, and narrowed down to the winning blend of select lots. The MJF blend is fruit-forward and perfect for hop-centric styles like pale ales, IPAs, and hazies. This blend also features a select lot of Citra¬Æ from our friends at Loza Farms here in the valley, the only Latino-owned hop farm in the nation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;‚ÄúQuality of course takes precedent when selecting hops, but it was also important to us to include hops from a farm owned by people of color,‚Äù said Garrett Oliver, President of the MJF. ‚ÄúThe Citra we blind-selected turned out to be from Loza, which is great. It integrates complex citrus and tropical notes to this blend, and we‚Äôre incredibly pleased with its inclusion.‚Äù&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Every pound includes a $5 donation&lt;/strong&gt; that John I. Haas made to the Michael James Jackson Foundation that will go towards scholarships for people of color who are continuing their education in the brewing industry.¬†&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The MJF was named the &lt;a title=&quot;2024 Nonprofit of the year&quot; href=&quot;https://vinepair.com/articles/2024-next-wave-michael-jackson-foundation-brewing-distilling/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;2024 nonprofit of the year by Vinepair&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you attending CBC this year in Indianapolis, stop by booth #2505 to try a collaboration beer from Two Locals Brewing in Philadelphia and MJF scholarship awardee Richard Koilor that features the MJF hop blend.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Try it for yourself today and brew up something amazing!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;product_description&quot;&gt;2025 MJF Hop Blend Brewing Values&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;product_description&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Selected Varieties (25% of each): &lt;/strong&gt;Citra¬Æ, Citra LUPOMAX¬Æ, Elani‚Ñ¢, El Dorado¬Æ&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Aroma:&lt;/strong&gt; Citrus, Melon, Sweet Fruit, Tropical, Grassy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
