&lt;span&gt; &quot;Hop variety and quality far exceeds my local homebrew stores. Nice touch on the zip top closure on the 2oz pouches. Whole cone is not available locally so it is a awesome you guys have so many options. Overall fantastic service and products. Will be ordering again for my next batch of brew.&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;review-header&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;review-header&quot;&gt;EXAMPLES OF BEERS BREWED WITH HALLERTAU MITTELFR√úH HOPS&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Brewers at Ninkasi use &lt;a href=&quot;https://web.archive.org/web/20241208113524/https://yakimavalleyhops.myshopify.com/products/magnum-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=german%20ma&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;German Magnums&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://web.archive.org/web/20241208113524/https://yakimavalleyhops.myshopify.com/products/saaz-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_sid=64e5b9953&amp;amp;_ss=r&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Saaz&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://web.archive.org/web/20241208113524/https://yakimavalleyhops.myshopify.com/products/tettnang-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=tettnag&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Tettnanger&lt;/a&gt;, and Hallertau Mittlefr√ºh together to achieve sweet, crisp, and refreshing pilsner.&lt;/p&gt;
