&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;product_description&quot;&gt;Euphorics Gift Pack&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 42, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sample Kit Requests are for approved Craft Accounts only‚Äîlimit of one per account please.¬† If more than one is added to your cart, we will contact you for your preference.¬† The sample kit is provided for free, but you must cover shipping.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;Available in 2 different variety packs that includes 5mL vials of various Euphorics‚Ñ¢ flavors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Boost your favorite beer, cocktail, or seltzer by simply giving your glass a spritz or two of any of the Euphorics‚Ñ¢ flavors. Or you could even get a little creative by mixing one or more flavors to create something complex and unique.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;There's a lot of flavor packed into this tiny kit. A little Euphorics goes a long way and depending on the beverage and dosing rate each 5mL vial can effectively flavor 1 barrel of beer, or 31 gallons.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;To use the sprayers, simply add one 5mL vial of Euphorics and top off with filtered water. Give it a quick shake and you're good to go! Store in the fridge between uses.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
