&lt;p&gt;&lt;span dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Typical Dosing Range in Beer:&lt;/strong&gt; 3mL - 7mL per barrel (31 gallons). Low end for lighter styles and high end for big IPAs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;From the manufacturer&lt;/strong&gt;: &quot;Introducing Euphorics‚Ñ¢, a highly concentrated, water-soluble flavor and aroma liquid product, made with 100% natural hops and botanicals. Made by brewers for brewers, Euphorics dramatically expands flavor and aroma possibilities while seamlessly integrating into beer and hop waters. Use on the cold side, post fermentation.&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Why use EUPHORICS‚Ñ¢: Layer after layer of flavor.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Amplified flavor spectrum&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Water soluble &amp;amp; ready to add&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;100% natural hops and botanicals&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly concentrated&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistent aroma and flavor&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
