&lt;p&gt;UK Golding is a suitable replacement for East Kent Golding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;product_description&quot;&gt;UK Golding Statistics:&lt;br&gt;Aroma: Floral, woody, spice, and citrus&lt;br&gt;Alpha Acids* 4.0 - 7.0 %&lt;br&gt;Beta Acids 2.0 - 3.0 % &lt;br&gt;Cohumulone 25 - 28 % of alpha acids &lt;br&gt;Total Oil 0.4 - 1.0 ml/100g &lt;br&gt;Myrcene 25 - 35 % of total oil &lt;br&gt;Humulene 34 - 45 % of total oil &lt;br&gt;Caryophyllene 13 - 16 % of total oil &lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All imported hop varieties are Type-90 hop pellets.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

