&lt;h5&gt;&lt;span itemprop=&quot;description&quot;&gt;See what brewers are saying about HBC 1019&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span itemprop=&quot;description&quot;&gt;This is the first year that HBC 1019 is really getting out there and into the hands of brewers. So if you brew with HBC 1019, be sure to leave a review and let us know what you think of it. What did you brew with it? How did it turn out? Would you brew with it again?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kettle Redi&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
