&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Crystal Hops Typical Analytical Range:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Alpha: 4.0-6.0%&lt;br&gt;Total Oil: 0.8 - 2.1 mL/100g&lt;br&gt;Myrcene: 40-65% of total oils&lt;br&gt;Humulene 18-24% of total oils&lt;br&gt;Caryophyllene 4-8% of total oils&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

