&lt;h1&gt;Elani Hops (YQH-1320 Hops)&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Elani Hop Profile - Previously YQH-1320&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div title=&quot;Page 1&quot; class=&quot;page&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;layoutArea&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;column&quot;&gt;Elani‚Ñ¢, previously known as YQH-1320, is a new hop variety from our friends at Yakima Quality Hops and is available for the first time in 2022. Elani is a found variety that Tim at YQH describes as &quot;Clean and bright. With tropical, citrus, and stone fruit.&quot; Sensory analysis of the 2022 crop picks out aromas of pineapple, guava, lime, white peach, and orange zest.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Elani Aroma:&lt;/strong&gt; Pineapple, guava, lime, white peach, orange zest&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Elani Typical Analytical Range&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Alpha: 9-11%&lt;br&gt;Total Oil: 1.3 - 2.0 mL/100g&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;group-range field-group-html-element&quot;&gt;2022 is the first commercial crop year for YQH-1320 hops.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;group-range field-group-html-element&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;Since this is the first year that YQH-1320 hops are available, be sure to leave a review&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;group-range field-group-html-element&quot;&gt;below to let us know what you think of them!&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;group-range field-group-html-element&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;group-range field-group-html-element&quot;&gt;See what brewers are saying about Elani hops:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;‚ÄúElani has been such a versatile hop for us. It shines very well by itself and plays extremely well with others. With big citrus notes and nice tropical undertones, I think you can expect to see Elani becoming a staple in many future recipes!‚Äù - Geoff Belcher, Head Brewer for &lt;a href=&quot;https://newrealmbrewing.com/&quot; title=&quot;New Realm Brewing&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;New Realm Brewing&lt;/a&gt;‚Äôs Charleston location &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The crew over at Br√ºlosophy brewed up a single hopped pale ale with Elani to better understand what it lends to a beer. &lt;a href=&quot;https://brulosophy.com/2024/09/16/the-hop-chronicles-elani-2023-pale-ale/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;Elani hop pale ale&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Read the full Elani sensory article here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

