&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description:&lt;/strong&gt; The product is an amber to brown free flowing liquid at temperatures above 32 ¬∞F (0 ¬∞C).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Concentration:&lt;/strong&gt; Standard concentration is 10.0 % +/- 0.5 hop resin components.&lt;/p&gt;
