&lt;li&gt;
&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-chevron-right text-color-xsdn-color&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Cohumulone: 22 ‚Äì 30%&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-chevron-right text-color-xsdn-color&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Total Oil (ml/100g): 0.5 ‚Äì 1.5%&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-chevron-right text-color-xsdn-color&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Humulene: 20 ‚Äì 30%&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-chevron-right text-color-xsdn-color&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Caryophyllene: 10 ‚Äì 20%&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-chevron-right text-color-xsdn-color&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Farnesene: 5 ‚Äì 10%&lt;/li&gt;
