&lt;br&gt;Since this is the first year that McKenzie‚Ñ¢ hops are available, be sure to leave a review below to let us know what you think of them!&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Stainless Steel Hop Addition Cups¬†&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Easily keep your hop additions neat and tidy with these stainless steel hop addition cups! You'll get a bundle of three cups that hold up to 8 oz. of hop pellets each.&lt;/p&gt;
