&lt;p&gt;Sonnet hops carry similar characteristics and flavor profiles as &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yakimavalleyhops.com/products/east-kent-golding-pellet-hops?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=east%20k&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; data-mce-fragment=&quot;1&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-mce-href=&quot;https://www.yakimavalleyhops.com/products/east-kent-golding-pellet-hops?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=east%20k&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot;&gt;East Kent Golding&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title=&quot;US Goldings&quot; href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.com/products/us-goldings-hop-pellets&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-mce-href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.com/products/us-goldings-hop-pellets&quot;&gt;US Golding&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yakimavalleyhops.com/products/hallertau-mittelfruh-pellet-hops?_pos=3&amp;amp;_psq=haller&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Hallertau Mittlefr√ºh&lt;/a&gt; making these hops an excellent substitution in your next recipe.¬†&lt;/p&gt;
