&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&quot;This was my first order from you guys, but it definitely won't be the last. Hops are packaged perfectly, and they smell so fresh! The perfect addition to my Pilsner.&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
