&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a title=&quot;Czech Pale Lager Homebrew Recipe&quot; href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.com/blogs/news/czech-pale-lager-homebrew-recipe&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Czech Pale Lager Recipe&lt;/a&gt;, by Robby Narquis, Chainsaw Brewing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Czech Saaz has also been identified as one of the &lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.com/blogs/news/mash-hopping-101&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;Hash Hopping&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Top Hops for Mash Hopping&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
