&lt;h3 class=&quot;review-header&quot;&gt;
&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;EXAMPLES OF BEERS BREWED WITH SAAZ HOPS&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;1.¬†&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.allagash.com/beer/white/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Allagash White - Allagash Brewing&lt;/a&gt;: Brewers at Allagash use¬†&lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.myshopify.com/products/nugget-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=nugget&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Nugget&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.com/products/crystal-hops&quot; title=&quot;Crystal Hops&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Crystal&lt;/a&gt;, and Saaz together to achieve a Begian-style wheat beer.¬†&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2.¬†&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.pfriembeer.com/beer/czech-dark-lager/#tasting-notes&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Czech Dark Lager - pFriem Brewing:&lt;/a&gt; Brewers at pFriem use¬†&lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.myshopify.com/products/perle-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=perle&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Perle&lt;/a&gt;, Saaz, and &lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.myshopify.com/products/tettnang-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=tett&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Tettnang&lt;/a&gt; together to achieve a dark beer with aromas bursting with flavor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3.¬†&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.deschutesbrewery.com/beer/the-dissident/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;The Dissident - Deschutes Brewing&lt;/a&gt;: Brewers at Deschutes use Saaz in a single hop for their Dissident Reserve series beer.&lt;/p&gt;
