&lt;p&gt;John I. Haas shares&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.johnihaas.com/blog/brewers-spotlight-equilibrium-brewing-lupomaxtm/&quot; data-mce-href=&quot;https://www.johnihaas.com/blog/brewers-spotlight-equilibrium-brewing-lupomaxtm/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt; Equilibrium Brewings&lt;/a&gt; thoughts on LUPO&lt;strong&gt;MAX&lt;/strong&gt; and their experiences.¬†&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our friends over at Valley Brewing used Citra LUPO&lt;strong&gt;MAX&lt;/strong&gt;, Sabro LUPO&lt;strong&gt;MAX&lt;/strong&gt;, and¬†Mosaic¬†LUPO&lt;strong&gt;MAX&lt;/strong&gt; together in the first ever commercial brewing recipe. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/p/CCuBtzbD1D3/&quot; data-mce-href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/p/CCuBtzbD1D3/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;LUPOMAX - Valley Brewing Co.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
