&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;product_description&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;SEE WHAT BREWERS ARE SAYING ABOUT MANDARINA BAVARIA&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;span&gt;Mandarina Bavaria - Wint H. 05/28/22&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
