&lt;h1&gt;Topaz Hops - Clementine Flavored Hop&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;Topaz‚Ñ¢ Hop Profile&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span itemprop=&quot;description&quot;&gt;Topaz‚Ñ¢ is a rare gem that has many different facets. It is definitely an efficient bittering hop that is high in alpha acids, but Topaz's bright and breezy nature shows in late additions and with dry hopping. In the boil Topaz‚Ñ¢ can present with &lt;strong&gt;resin&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.com/products/talus-hop-pellets&quot; title=&quot;pine hop flavor&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;pine&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but there are light fruit flavors of &lt;strong&gt;lychee&lt;/strong&gt; and clementines from low heat applications.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Thinking about using Aussie hops for the first time or trying something different? Download this amazing little &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.hops.com.au/beer-recipe-book/&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;recipe book&lt;/a&gt;, HPA has put together to get your creative juices flowing!¬†&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;product_description&quot; itemprop=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/h5&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Galaxy Hop Pellets&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;Galaxy Hop Profile: Passionfruit - Peach - Citrus&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Galaxy¬Æ hops are currently one of the most sought-after hop varieties in the world. Galaxy¬Æ hops are prized for their big aromas of peach, guava, and oranges. Galaxy¬Æ hops are perfect in hazy IPAs and works well with the usual suspects of&lt;span&gt;¬†&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a title=&quot;Citra Hop Pellets&quot; href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.com/products/citra-hop-pellets&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Citra&lt;/a&gt;¬Æ and&lt;span&gt;¬†&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a title=&quot;Mosaic Hop Pellets&quot; href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.com/products/mosaic-hop-pellets&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Mosaic&lt;/a&gt;¬Æ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;Galaxy Description from the Grower&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&quot;World-famous flavours of punchy passionfruit, juicy peach and tangy citrus. The high concentration of essential oils and alpha acids make these flavours more distinct through late addition in the kettle, whirlpool or dry hopping.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h6&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Thinking about using Aussie hops for the first time or trying something different? Download this amazing little &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.hops.com.au/beer-recipe-book/&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;recipe book&lt;/a&gt;, HPA has put together to get your creative juices flowing!¬†&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h6&gt;
