&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #303847;&quot; color=&quot;#303847&quot;&gt;2.¬†&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.drubru.com/beer/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #303847;&quot;&gt;Dru-Bru - Hazy¬†IPA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Brewers at Dru Bru use BRU-1 and a pair of experimental hops (HBC 586 &amp;amp; HBC 630)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #303847;&quot;&gt;3.¬†&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.dogfish.com/blog/hazy-o-our-new-hazy-ipa-made-four-types-oats-and-its-oooohh-so-juicy&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Dogfish Head Craft Brewery - Hazy-O!&lt;/a&gt;: Brewers at Dogfish Head use¬†&lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.myshopify.com/products/citra-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=citra&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Citra&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.myshopify.com/products/mosaic-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=mosa&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Mosaic&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.myshopify.com/products/azacca-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=azacc&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Azacca&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.myshopify.com/products/centennial-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=cent&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Centennial&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.myshopify.com/products/simcoe-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=simco&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Simcoe&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.myshopify.com/products/sabro-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=Sabr&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Sabro&lt;/a&gt;, and BRU-1 together to create a silky smooth Hazy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.dogfish.com/blog/hazy-o-our-new-hazy-ipa-made-four-types-oats-and-its-oooohh-so-juicy&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #303847;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #303847;&quot;&gt;BRU-1 HOP SUBSTITUTIONS¬†&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #303847;&quot;&gt;BRU-1 has lots of similar characteristics as &lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.com/products/vic-secret-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=vic%20secre&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Vic Secret&lt;/a&gt;¬†and¬†&lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.com/products/talus-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=talus&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Talus&lt;/a&gt;, making them the perfect substitutions.¬†Both hops are very fruity, pineapple forward, and great for dry hopping. Use &lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.com/products/vic-secret-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=vic%20se&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Vic Secret&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=&quot;https://yakimavalleyhops.com/products/talus-hop-pellets?_pos=1&amp;amp;_psq=talus&amp;amp;_ss=e&amp;amp;_v=1.0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Talus&lt;/a&gt; in your next beer!¬†&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
